```
@JsonTypeInfo(use = NAME, property = &quot;type&quot;)
@JsonSubTypes(
  @Type(MyClass1.class, name = &quot;MyClass1&quot;),
  @Type(MyClass2.class, name = &quot;MyClass2&quot;)
)
public class BaseClass {
  String id;
}
```

You may also want to look into other values for [`use`](https://fasterxml.github.io/jackson-annotations/javadoc/2.9/com/fasterxml/jackson/annotation/JsonTypeInfo.Id.html), such as `CLASS` or `MINIMAL_CLASS`.

