To mock all calls of `originalMethod` regardless the passed integer, you can use `anyInt()`. To call the `differentMethod` you can extract the passed integer with `invocation.getArgument(..)`. In summary it could look like this:

```java
when(mock.originalMethod(anyInt())).thenAnswer(invocation -&gt; {
    int theInt = invocation.getArgument(0, int.class);
    return mock.differentMethod(theInt);
});
```

